title: X-MAS FLASHBACK CONCERT
desc: Ensino Presents X-Mas FlashBack Concert on Sat. Dec. 26th. 2015 at the LongShoreman Hall in Wilmington, Ca. Come and experience a up close and personal concert/party with 2 dance floors: Featuring 80's and 90's Freestyle and Hip Hop performances by: DEBBIE DEB, TRINERE,RAPPIN4TAY,MELLOW MAN ACE Along with DJ PInky,Dj G3O playing ?Funk,Disco,and old school Hip Hop!!
